om\": 950, \"to\": 968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During Thursday's competition at the University of the District of Columbia, DeMarco mentioned Olympic star Katie Ledecky, regarded as a \\\"longtime member\\\" of the Horizons community who has visited with students taking part in the program.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1079, \"end\": 1092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Thursday's competition\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"the University\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"the District\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1034}, {\"ngram\": \"Columbia\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1046}, {\"ngram\": \"DeMarco\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1055}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"longtime member\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1124}, {\"ngram\": \"the Horizons community\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"students\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1181}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1193}, {\"ngram\": \"the program\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Regarding the issue of equity and who has access to swimming facilities and swimming instruction, DeMarco said, \\\"Katie Ledecky came to visit us a few summers ago and she said something that's always stuck with me.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1324, \"end\": 1337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the issue\", \"from\": 122