.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the link\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2148}, {\"ngram\": \"Horizons\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2162}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"the eight-time gold medalist\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2235}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2275}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2283}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because she's not even that old and she's already accomplished so much, and I hope to do the same.\\\"\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2384, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While he's an admirer of Ledecky, his professional plans include a career outside the pool.\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2477, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an admirer\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2407}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2418}, {\"ngram\": \"his professional plans\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2442}, {\"ngram\": \"a career\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2459}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hernandez has plans to become a defense attorney.\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2478, \"end\": 2487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\", \"score\": 0.7544329697359324, \"rank\": 0.12361940355195014, \"text\": \"Hernandez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"plans\", \"from\": 2492, \"to\": 2497}, {\"ngram\": \"a defense attorney\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hernandez admitted getting butterflies before racing, but said he always considers his effort: \\\"Once I get out, I feel really confident.\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2529, \"end\": 2538, \"title\": \"http://db